Finally, we use the runContinuously() function to run the stepper motor continuously.

Note: Make sure to adjust the step, direction, and enable pins in the code to match your stepper motor driver. Also, note that the ContinuousStepper library has some limitations on the motor speed range and acceleration time, so make sure to read the documentation carefully.

